{"data": [{"id": "4742848", "title": "BNY Mellon Global Fixed Income Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Isolate currency on golden coin stacking include dollar euro pound sterling yen and yuan with world on white background for currency exchange concept ,Element of this image from NASA and 3d render.\" data-id=\"1429634204\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dilok Klaisataporn</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>\u201cMonetary policy easing is expected to continue through the final quarter of the year and into 2025. While recession is a clear risk, it is not our central case, although central banks have plenty of scope to cut rates if</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1429634204/image_1429634204.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742848-bny-mellon-global-fixed-income-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 10:59:00"}, {"id": "4742846", "title": "GameStop: It's Time To Wave Bye Bye To This Stock Once And For All", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Girl painting \"game over\" text on wall' data-id=\"2150983182\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Is the video game rettail business amelting ice cube vs online games?</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>GME expected to release 4Q24 earnings (FY October) on Dec. 10</h2> <p>There seems to be a supreme irony implicit in the possible</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983182/image_2150983182.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742846-gamestop-wave-bye-bye-to-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 10:43:18"}, {"id": "4742842", "title": "PDO: How Good Is This 11% Yield?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Yield Road Sign Post Over a Blue Sky\" data-id=\"155095389\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5600px\" height=\"3743px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ryasick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Article Thesis</h2> <p>PIMCO Dynamic Income Opportunities Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PDO\" title=\"PIMCO Dynamic Income Opportunities Fund\">PDO</a></span>) is a closed-end fund that invests in fixed-income assets and that offers a very generous dividend yield of around 11% at current prices. But a high dividend yield alone is not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742842-pdo-how-good-is-11-percent-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 10:10:47"}, {"id": "4742840", "title": "EQIN: A Good Value ETF, But Value Still Is Out Of Style", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wooden seesaw scale empty on wooden sphere on wood table with wording VALUE and PRICE balancing\" data-id=\"1303850380\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"3898px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">marchmeena29</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>EQIN strategy</h2> <p>Columbia U.S. Equity Income ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EQIN\" title=\"Columbia U.S. Equity Income ETF\">EQIN</a></span>) is an actively managed ETF launched on 6/13/2016. It has a portfolio of 100 stocks, a 30-day SEC yield of 2.24%, and an expense ratio of 0.35%.</p> <p>As described in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742840-eqin-good-value-etf-but-value-still-out-of-style", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:55:27"}, {"id": "4742843", "title": "Week Ahead: 4 G10 Central Banks Meet, 3 To Cut, Brazil To Hike 75 Bp And U.S. CPI May Hold Key To FOMC", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Putting a coin in a white piggy bank at home.\" data-id=\"1363128263\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Guido Mieth</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The US dollar advanced against all the G10 currencies last week but the Swiss franc turned in a most mixed performance against emerging market currencies. The US 10-year yield fell for the third consecutive week and near 4.16%, it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363128263/image_1363128263.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742843-week-ahead-4-g10-central-banks-meet-3-to-cut-brazil-to-hike-75-bp-and-us-cpi-may-hold-key-to-fomc", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:40:00"}, {"id": "4742838", "title": "ArcBest Corporation: An Upgrade Isn't Far Off If Shares Keep Falling Like This", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ABF Freight Systems trucks\" data-id=\"1182783632\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5349px\" height=\"3566px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The last several months have not been particularly pleasant for shareholders of logistics firm <strong>ArcBest Corporation</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARCB\" title=\"ArcBest Corporation\">ARCB</a></span>). Back in March of this year, I decided to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4675588-arcbest-the-wonderful-ride-has-come-to-an-end-for-now\">downgrade</a> the stock from a \u2018buy\u2019 to a \u2018hold\u2019. That downgrade was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1182783632/image_1182783632.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742838-arcbest-upgrade-not-far-off-if-shares-keep-falling", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:24:26"}, {"id": "4742837", "title": "Huntington Ingalls Industries: Staying Afloat", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/dv144013/photo/group-of-ships-in-persian-gulf-including-uss-john-f-kennedy-aircraft-carrier.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=F5W0I0o_Iu1QnZieD6PgSrRPgehCGjST873Rua3gpks=\" alt=\"Group of ships in Persian Gulf, including USS John F Kennedy (CV-67) Aircraft Carrier\" data-id=\"dv144013\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Frank Rossoto Stocktrek/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h3>Company Description</h3> <p>Huntington Ingalls Industries (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HII\" title=\"Huntington Ingalls Industries, Inc.\">HII</a></span>) participates in the design, building and maintenance of military ships. The shipbuilding giant is separated into three segments, Ingalls Shipbuilding, Newport News Shipbuilding and Technical Solutions. HII formed via a spin-off</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742837-huntington-ingalls-staying-afloat", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:18:06"}, {"id": "4742836", "title": "Kayne Anderson: Defensive BDC Overlooked By The Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A US Dollar symbol made of wood with leaves growing from it.\" data-id=\"1455774438\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Kayne Anderson BDC (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KBDC\" title=\"Kayne Anderson BDC, Inc.\">KBDC</a></span>) is a newcomer to the stock market, having started trading in Q2 2024. <a href=\"https://s204.q4cdn.com/976242841/files/doc_financials/2024/q3/KBDC_3Q-24_Investor-Presentation_2024-11-14_vFINAL.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">As of September 30, 2024</a>, its portfolio value amounted to $1.94B. KBDC concentrates on middle-market businesses, generating between $10m and $50m in EBITDA</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742836-kayne-anderson-defensive-bdc-overlooked-by-the-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:11:55"}, {"id": "4742834", "title": "ASML: One Of The Strongest Buys Due To Its Huge Monopoly", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt